{
 "name": "RPlog_Meals_and_Deals",
 "title": "Meals and Deals on Nar Shaddaa",
 "summary": "On the landing platforms of the city-moon Nar Shaddaa, the smuggler Jaspar reunites with the diminutive Sullustan mechanic Jae Ten, who has been eagerly inspecting Jaspar's freighter, the Hirakiis. After Jae fusses over the ship, the pair head down to the smoky Meltdown Cafe for ale and meat. Over their meal Jaspar lays out a job he is planning with a supplier friend who claims to have a lucrative catch lined up. Jae, delighted by food and the promise of credits, toasts to the venture as the two cement their partnership.",
